{"tid":1464172,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"救人係救護員職責同專業！","createTime":"2019-08-13T14:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T15:09:08.000Z","uid":109770,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bbacdf4470354a26c284211220e1fc5dc1a6340e","tid":1464172,"uid":109770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:33:34.000Z","msg":"可以比你地屌左先，我唔係現場，但睇live可以話應該睇得清過現場外圍嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n條深圳公安狗扮暈，救護員到現場處理，有位巴打一直叫人擋住唔比救護員走，又同救護員講話咩你而家救佢一個香港會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我只希望你地認清 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">救人係佢地嘅職責，亦係佢地嘅專業</span><br />\n<br />\n唔撚係幫公安狗，你一係係救護員黎之前就打撚死佢，而家佢地接手，唔應該留難呢班由6月開始一直救我地手足嘅人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對敵人仁慈，由無當場打死佢，己經係仁慈。而家救護員到場，唔應該要佢地做磨心</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係現場，可以比你地隨便屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但真係希望現場睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbdc28d9ac7b90f50974e1ccf047a311fcbd3bd1","tid":1464172,"uid":109770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:34:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecf2ea4ea54ebcca97f9d8b3333894a9b4180b12","tid":1464172,"uid":109770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:34:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea63d28924bc776266def9d765215305609110ed","tid":1464172,"uid":109770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:34:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b6f4a03811409a401580f8c65f804017f48a1e2","tid":1464172,"uid":109770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:35:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a06db265722f7f29c7d179adc02d556d661ad23","tid":1464172,"uid":109770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:36:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c4ae2de82dfd759556eac55e7607ba9d98337ce","tid":1464172,"uid":109770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:37:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b1309c86c767418bfeb4f5e2a81752774785cd0","tid":1464172,"uid":109770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:37:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d21f27aa97f006d26445a80793526ed6baa64c","tid":1464172,"uid":109770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:37:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2180803bf0f53b5e9ac1cd9bf0e33f9ce52b3ec1","tid":1464172,"uid":109770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:37:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67af2a5a6c290676780faa3d721867d8f95f7b70","tid":1464172,"uid":109770,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:38:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89606890aec351ee8d4e61bb4174f5da2ded014d","tid":1464172,"uid":109770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:42:45.000Z","msg":"自推十次，唉，此帖己完。"},{"pid":"afd0ff950c8a1e1cba1cdca6419e317d73f1261e","tid":1464172,"uid":207087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:48:17.000Z","msg":"做得臥底的公安，體質有冇咁差？救護人員不是醫生，詐死你分唔到，即場用amonia （？）整醒佢，完全冇反應即是做戲！"},{"pid":"a400104f08faf8833aa871a25170ad4705ac3f7a","tid":1464172,"uid":109770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"afd0ff950c8a1e1cba1cdca6419e317d73f1261e","tid":1464172,"uid":207087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:48:17.000Z","msg":"做得臥底的公安，體質有冇咁差？救護人員不是醫生，詐死你分唔到，即場用amonia （？）整醒佢，完全冇反應即是做戲！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:54:13.000Z","msg":"體質唔差，係要解決佢點解唔係救護到之前做。而家救護接手，點解要佢地做磨心呢？隻公安狗比人圍，唔係呢一時三刻嘅事，前線想打佢洩憤？想打死佢？想開記者會？想做乜都唔撚知，救護接哂手，咁可以點？ 留低阻止救援呢個不人道罪名？ 何況班救護6月以黎多次救我地手足，班狗擋一擋架車都比我地屌到仆街，點解而家做左我地反抗對象嘅行為？<br />\n如果你係話想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢嘅，機會今日擺到明冇左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a929f9bfc96a0193a023246971974920b9f2942","tid":1464172,"uid":207087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:02:46.000Z","msg":"1. 冇表面傷痕<br />\n2. 呼吸和心跳無明顯異狀<br />\n3. 憑什麼要即時送院<br />\n4. 有疑慮可以叫真正醫生到埸，胡亂移動所謂傷者亦有機會令情況惡化"},{"pid":"3e44cafdbb789eeecd8ecd4501ed84d38f14eab6","tid":1464172,"uid":109770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a929f9bfc96a0193a023246971974920b9f2942","tid":1464172,"uid":207087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:02:46.000Z","msg":"1. 冇表面傷痕<br />\n2. 呼吸和心跳無明顯異狀<br />\n3. 憑什麼要即時送院<br />\n4. 有疑慮可以叫真正醫生到埸，胡亂移動所謂傷者亦有機會令情況惡化"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:06:43.000Z","msg":"第三題你都問得出口？ 憑咩即時送院？因為佢身份就唔可以即時送院？<br />\n<br />\n我真心唔撚係話幫隻狗，個問題係而家呢個timing唔上唔落圍救護，引來大批狗，準備送頭？"},{"pid":"27edb58bfc312982a98eddd25291f2924367760c","tid":1464172,"uid":109770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T15:09:08.000Z","msg":"由救護接手一刻開始，留佢係度有乜野用？<br />\n要影嘅資訊影哂出哂<br />\n留佢係度，除咗係比藉口班狗武力清場<br />\n仲有乜用？"}]}